The global hydrophobic coatings market is expected to witness substantial growth during the forecast period of 2021 to 2030. Numerous factors are driving the market, including the increasing demand for hydrophobic coatings in various industries such as automotive, aerospace, and building & construction. The ability of these coatings to repel water and other liquids effectively, thereby offering protection from corrosion, UV radiation, and wear and tear, is a significant factor fueling their adoption. Moreover, the growing focus on sustainability and eco-friendly products is further boosting the market for hydrophobic coatings.

